インタフェース Damageable

  • すべてのスーパーインタフェース:

    既知のサブインタフェースのリスト:
    Ageable, Ambient, Animals, ArmorStand, Bat, Blaze, CaveSpider, Chicken, ComplexLivingEntity, Cow, Creature, Creeper, EnderDragon, EnderDragonPart, Enderman, Endermite, Flying, Ghast, Giant, Golem, Guardian, Horse, HumanEntity, IronGolem, LivingEntity, MagmaCube, Monster, MushroomCow, NPC, Ocelot, Pig, PigZombie, Player, Rabbit, Sheep, Shulker, Silverfish, Skeleton, Slime, Snowman, Spider, Squid, Villager, WaterMob, Witch, Wither, Wolf, Zombie

    public interface Damageable
extends Entity
    Represents an Entity that has health and can take damage.

void _INVALID_damage(int amount)

      • setMaxHealth

        void setMaxHealth(double health)
        Sets the maximum health this entity can have.

        If the health of the entity is above the value provided it will be set to that value.

        Note: An entity with a health bar (Player, EnderDragon, Wither, etc...} will have their bar scaled accordingly.

        パラメータ:
        health - amount of health to set the maximum to
